  system. Subsequently, the assistant enhanced API routes by adding input
  validation for pagination parameters and implementing limits for CSV exports
  to prevent memory issues. It also corrected PDF generation logic to accurately
  calculate sleep metrics, handling empty time inputs and incorporating minutes.
  Finally, it improved number input fields to allow null values and made the
  "Download PDF" button functional.
